Member Services

        Notice No. 00-84

        February 6, 2001


COMMODITY EXCHANGE, INC.


TERMINATION OF TRADING PRIVILEGES


 Please be advised that the Exchange has been notified by Spear, Leeds, &

Kellogg that effective with the close of business February 5, 2001, they will

no longer guarantee the membership(s) of Jacqueline Solvino (LINA-6075).


 Therefore, in accordance with the Exchange Rule 4.12, the trading privileges

of the aforementioned individual(s) are hereby suspended until such time as a

new primary clearing member guarantee is provided.


 In connection therewith, notification of any claims against the

aforementioned individuals arising out of transactions executed on the

Exchange up to the close of business on February 5, 2001, must be submitted

to the Corporate Secretary,s Office within ten (10) days.


